714546f-a.title: Manhattan: 78th Street (East) - 3rd Avenue
714546f-a.text:
169-171 East 78h Street, (xcavation) north side, between Third and
Lexington Aves. Also shown is a rear view of Nos. 176-184 East 79th Street,
south side, betweAn Third and Lexington Aves. Note new building being
erected on the north side of 79th. Street. Building with sign is the
Manhattan Storage Warehouse.
February 2, 1928.
P2 L, Sperr.

714547f-a.title: Manhattan: 78th Street (East) - 3rd Avenue
714547f-a.text:
East 78th Street, south side, west from Third to and including Lew
ington Aves. Note demolition at the S.W. corner of Third Ave.
September 8, 1936.
P. L. Sperr.
